PayJunction,is,a,secure,credit,card,processing,service,Users,of,PayJunction,can,accept,credit,card,payments,on,their,websites,in,their,offices,stores,and,via,mobile,phones,The,PayJunction,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,PayJunction,with,other,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,retrieving,receipts,and,electronic,signatures,managing,payments,and,accessing,customer,details